Package: promillo
Type: Package
Title: Computation and Visualization of Body Alcohol Concentration (BAC)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marianna Plesiak [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Marianna Plesiak <mariannaplesiak207@ukr.net>
Description: Functions to compute the Body Alcohol 
  Concentration index depending on the amount of consumed alcohol, drinking time 
  and personal data as well as a function for visualizing of the BAC reduction 
  within a drinking time period.
Imports: checkmate, ggplot2, lubridate
Suggests: testthat
